---
<footer class="px-2 lg:px-4 py-2.5 max-w-7xl mx-auto py-7 text-center lg:text-left">
    <div class="py-3 border-t-2 border-gray-200">
        <div class="sm:flex sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
            <span class="block mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-500">Â© 2023 Matt Bourne - All Rights Reserved.</span>
            <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center lg:mt-1 mt-3 justify-center lg:justify-end">
                <li>
                    <a class="lg:p-1 p-3 lg:px-4 text-xl leading-6 text-gray-500 hover:text-brand-blue transition ease-in-out duration-150" href="mailto:hello@mattbourne.co.uk"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i></a>
